423
00:27:10,309 --> 00:27:11,752
Oleh itu, saya, Kwon Jung Rok,

424
00:27:11,777 --> 00:27:13,409
minta awak, Oh Jin Sim,

425
00:27:13,434 --> 00:27:16,485
